<div class="scp-image-block block-center" style="width:100%;"><img src="http://scp-wiki.wdfiles.com/local--files/fragment:scp-4338-2/SCP-4338v2.jpg" style="width:100%;" alt="SCP-4338v2.jpg" class="image" />
<div class="scp-image-caption" style="width:100%;">
<p>SCP-4338. Still-frame taken from drone footage of Event DN-4338-43, 11/08/2018.</p>
</div>
